item.title: Photo Contest
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded: Christine is holding a contest at her website to see if someone can give her the name of a particular flower she took a picture of on our honeymoon. Winner receives a 5X7 signed print of the particular photograph.
